pbmc <- NormalizeData(pbmc, 
                      normalization.method = \LogNormalize\, 
                      scale.factor = 10000, 
                      verbose = FALSE)

                             selection.method = \mean.var.plot\, 
                             nfeatures = 2000, 
                             mean.cutoff=c(0.5, Inf), 
                             dispersion.cutoff=c(0.5, Inf),
